query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `asset_timeline_events` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `assetId` int NOT NULL,
  `projectId` int NOT NULL,
  `eventType` enum('assessment','deficiency','maintenance','document','schedule','custom') NOT NULL,
  `eventDate` timestamp NOT NULL,
  `title` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `relatedId` int,
  `metadata` text,
  `createdBy` int,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `asset_timeline_events_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  INDEX `idx_asset_timeline` (`assetId`, `eventDate`),
  INDEX `idx_event_type` (`eventType`)
)
